{
  "texts": [
    "Table 5 represents the deep learning-based analysis of 80% learning rate.",
    "It achieves this with the DeepEnrollNet al.ways outperforming all other deep learning models, CNN, MLP, LSTM, and DNN, using 80% of the learning data in terms of all the metrics R², MSE, MSRE, NMSE, RMSE, and MAPE.",
    "This suggests that the robust and effective algorithm captures the underline pattern in the data effectively along with a minimum prediction error.",
    "The R² maximum value, for the DeepEnrollNet, has the best value at 0.98765.",
    "The DeepEnrollNet reaches an all-time high R² of 0.98765, indicating that the model explains most of the variance present in the data under consideration."
  ]
}